<p>PythonGuru is a self-learning platform for learning Python language.</p>

<h2 id="author">Author</h2>

<p><a href="https://freelancerbrg.com/">Budh Ram Gurung or simply BRG</a> is the owner of this platform.
He is a self-taught software engineer and have 8.5+ years of IT industry experience.
He belief that <em>self-learning is the best learning approach</em>.</p>

<p>And, hence, to promote <em>self-learning</em> attitude he has started this platform so that those
who want to learn by themselves can able to learn through this platform.</p>

